app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The following are available online at https://www.mdpi.com/2036-7449/13/1/2/s1, Supplementary material 1 (Figure S1) is a timeline of the present case. Supplementary material 2 (Figure S2) is a figure with the genetic sequences used for the identification of the etiologic agent ( Fusarium graminearum complex).
